title: Chris Paul-Russell Westbrook, duo grades, and Sam Presti
itunes:title: Chris Paul-Russell Westbrook, duo grades, and Sam Presti
description:
Colin breaks down the Chris Paul-Russell Westbrook trade, and who actually won. His grades for the top duos in the NBA, and why Thunder GM Sam Presti could learn a thing or two from Patriots HC Bill Belichick. Guests include Chris Broussard, Kendrick Perkins, Matt Barnes, Stephen Jackson, and Jason McIntyre.
